item.description:
Our DOUBLE HEALING CIRCLE happens on the fourth Wednesday of each month.  This is a chance for members of the community to learn about various healing modalities.  After each discussion, we create a healing circle so that all can give/receive hands-on healing.

 

This month we welcome Mary Ellen Tero will be speaking on the ancient healing art of Ear Coning/Candling.  Mary Ellen is both a practitioner and teacher of this art.  Come learn about the benefits of Ear Coning. 

If there is interest, we may be able to host a class on it in the near future.
